🎯 What is Observability in MLOps?
👉 Observability = understanding model + system behavior in real time
In MLOps, we monitor:
Data → Model → API → Infrastructure

Real MLOps Observability Architecture (Your Case)
KServe Model API
      ↓
Dynatrace OneAgent
      ↓
Collect:
  - Latency
  - Errors
  - Throughput

Azure ML
      ↓
